    "en": {
      "title": "The prime minister played under the influence of alcohol",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Finland's female Prime Minister Sanna Marin has come under heavy criticism after a video of her drunken friends doing punches was released.",
        "Sanna Marin is the Prime Minister of Finland's ruling Social Democratic Party. In this case, a video of Channa Marin playing a game after drinking alcohol with her friends in an apartment is going viral on social media.",
        "There has been a strong protest among the people of the country as they have acted in a way that disrespects and tarnishes the post of Prime Minister. The media is also criticizing."
      ],
